WEBVTT

00:05:28.999 --> 00:05:30.660
of gun violence;

00:05:30.684 --> 00:05:32.844
blocking pediatricians
from talking to parents

00:05:32.868 --> 00:05:34.679
about the dangers of guns in the home;

00:05:34.703 --> 00:05:37.072
blocking smart-gun technology
and other technology

00:05:37.096 --> 00:05:39.767
that would prevent kids
from firing parents' guns

00:05:39.791 --> 00:05:41.354
and would save lives.

00:05:41.812 --> 00:05:44.081
They're desperate to hide the truth,

00:05:44.105 --> 00:05:48.383
because they view the truth
as a threat to their bottom line.

00:05:48.407 --> 00:05:49.568
And every day,

00:05:49.592 --> 00:05:51.187
people are dying as a result.

00:05:51.211 --> 00:05:53.702
And a lot of those people are children.

00:05:54.108 --> 00:05:56.445
Every day in the US,

00:05:56.469 --> 00:05:59.658
nine kids are just shot unintentionally.